high_descs: Walk to the end of the kitchen island with the head of lettuce on it.
Pick up the head of lettuce.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.

Open the fridge door, place the head of lettuce in the middle of the shelf with a potato to its left and close the fridge door; after cooling, open the fridge door, pick up the lettuce and close the fridge door.
Turn around and walk to the green bin to the left of the stove on the other side of the room.
Put the lettuce in the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate a head of lettuce, place it in the green bin

high_descs: Go straight ahead, and then turn left to face the short side of the island.
Pick up the green vegetable close to the edge.
Carry the vegetable and turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the vegetable inside. Shut the door. Open the fridge and take the vegetable out and shut the door.
Carry the vegetable and turn around. Go straight and then turn left and right to find the trash can on the floor.
Place the vegetable in the trash car.
anns.task_desc: Move a vegetable to the fridge and then the trash.

high_descs: Go left and stand in front of the island with a knife and lettuce on it.
Pick the lettuce up from the counter.
Turn to the left to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and close the door and then open the door and pick up the lettuce.
Turn around and the go left and then turn right to face the trash can.
Put the lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce in the trash can.
